- Great admirer.
- Nice to meet you. Thanks.

491
00:35:19,642 --> 00:35:21,034
Where's the team?

492
00:35:42,607 --> 00:35:44,302
How are you doing, fellas?

493
00:35:52,517 --> 00:35:54,725
- Coach.
- How are you doing, Tinker?

494
00:35:57,802 --> 00:35:59,362
Good evening, gentlemen.

495
00:36:00,498 --> 00:36:01,798
Good to see you.

496
00:36:03,494 --> 00:36:04,495
Listen...

497
00:36:06,262 --> 00:36:08,123
Last week, we got our asses beat

498
00:36:08,292 --> 00:36:11,168
doing our best,
there is no shame in that, gentlemen.

499
00:36:11,854 --> 00:36:13,670
But I'll tell you what,
I've got shame.

500
00:36:14,336 --> 00:36:16,715
I've got shame
and I apologize to you.

501
00:36:18,655 --> 00:36:21,637
I apologize
for not giving you the chance

502
00:36:21,805 --> 00:36:23,355
to finish your fight.

503
00:36:25,753 --> 00:36:27,863
I wanna finish that fight with you.

504
00:36:28,363 --> 00:36:31,363
And I'm asking you,
right here, right now,

505
00:36:31,488 --> 00:36:33,941
to allow me to help you
finish that fight.

506
00:37:03,490 --> 00:37:04,990
See this, gentlemen?

507
00:37:05,724 --> 00:37:07,558
This right here, this is the past.

508
00:37:13,720 --> 00:37:15,644
Who wants to finish this fight?

509
00:37:17,231 --> 00:37:19,361
Who'll finish this fight with me?

510
00:37:52,505 --> 00:37:53,605
I will, sir.

511
00:38:09,121 --> 00:38:11,321
Glad to have you on board, Tinker.

512
00:38:18,223 --> 00:38:19,523
Let's finish it.

513
00:38:21,005 --> 00:38:22,305
Let's finish it!

514
00:38:24,638 --> 00:38:26,138
Let's do this, boys!

515
00:38:41,242 --> 00:38:42,342
Hey, sailor.

516
00:38:45,892 --> 00:38:48,152
Looks like
you haven't slept in a week.

517
00:38:49,555 --> 00:38:50,805
Feels that way.

518
00:38:54,810 --> 00:38:56,708
Kinda looking for a place
if you know any.

519
00:38:57,234 --> 00:38:58,585
It shouldn't be so hard.

520
00:38:58,753 --> 00:39:00,671
It is when you don't have
first and last.

521
00:39:06,789 --> 00:39:09,638
I do have this trailer...
in my backyard.

522
00:39:12,359 --> 00:39:14,227
I'll charge you a $100 a month.

523
00:39:14,352 --> 00:39:16,725
You can stay there
until you find a place.

524
00:39:19,966 --> 00:39:21,149
It's very sweet.

525
00:39:22,218 --> 00:39:25,361
Don't get me wrong,
that was unbelievable,

526
00:39:25,822 --> 00:39:28,782
but I'm not that into you.

527
00:39:29,641 --> 00:39:33,036
More importantly, you're not into me,
so who really needs to go there, right?

528
00:39:33,755 --> 00:39:35,998
I'm not gonna come
banging on your door

529
00:39:36,166 --> 00:39:38,861
in the middle of the night,
you know what I mean?

530
00:39:39,125 --> 00:39:40,618
But I could use the cash.

531
00:39:41,371 --> 00:39:42,371
When?

532
00:39:44,478 --> 00:39:45,778
Start right now.

533
00:39:46,092 --> 00:39:48,176
- Let me get you the keys.
- Like tonight?

534
00:39:48,344 --> 00:39:49,944
Remember where I live?

535
00:39:50,221 --> 00:39:52,508
I'm gonna give my daughter a call.

536
00:39:53,767 --> 00:39:55,600
She's not gonna know you from Adam.

537
00:39:56,604 --> 00:39:58,601
I don't want you to scare her.

538
00:40:03,361 --> 00:40:04,452
Here you go.

539
00:40:06,278 --> 00:40:07,278
Thank you.

540
00:41:05,484 --> 00:41:06,934
What are you doing?

541
00:41:08,080 --> 00:41:09,280
Drinking wine.

542
00:41:21,532 --> 00:41:22,632
How are you?

543
00:41:26,109 --> 00:41:28,009
How did everything go today?

544
00:41:33,886 --> 00:41:36,160
I got booed at the pep rally.

545
00:41:37,211 --> 00:41:38,861
What do you mean booed?

546
00:41:41,130 --> 00:41:42,282
I mean booed.

547
00:41:51,829 --> 00:41:54,629
But I did get one little bit
of satisfaction.

548
00:41:57,334 --> 00:42:00,950
Just being able to stand up
to those good old boys,

549
00:42:01,344 --> 00:42:02,994
Joe McCoy and his crew.

550
00:42:06,561 --> 00:42:08,277
So I got that going for me.

551
00:42:08,402 --> 00:42:09,500
And wine.

552
00:42:15,923 --> 00:42:17,273
How was your day?

553
00:42:20,014 --> 00:42:21,264
They showed up.

554
00:42:22,760 --> 00:42:23,760
They did?

555
00:42:25,288 --> 00:42:26,438
It's a start.

556
00:42:27,412 --> 00:42:28,563
That's great.

557
00:42:35,658 --> 00:42:37,008
I'm sorry I lied.

558
00:42:39,148 --> 00:42:40,148
I know.

